org.jfree.base.log

Class DefaultLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jfree.util.Log
      • org.jfree.base.log.DefaultLog

  • public class DefaultLog
extends Log
    A default log implementation. The Log class defines how to create Logger-contexts and how to forward messages to the logtargets.
    Author:
    Thomas Morgner
